i really need to go on here more i think.  well guys how are you all? so much has happened since i have last updated this so i think i should start writing in here more often so its easier to remember things.  hmmmm well i had a boyfriend for a month in like august/ september.  he broke up with me for my best friend so i was not too happy bout that.  i'm at south downs now not 6th form and although i liked it at 6th form cause of all the friends i made, south downs is so much better. i have learned more at south downs than i did for the whole year at 6th form which just is not right.  but oh well.  im the only girl in my class and so that makes the rest of the class consisting of 16 guys. hmmm. any one else feeling weird bout that?  oh well. then there was what happened on monday. it was cool in the way that i got a lift home in a police car but not in the way that i was scared shitless the whole time.  my friend got in a fight with her dad's new gf who used to be her best friend.  her dad's new gf has only just turned 18 and her dad is 39. and not only that its rumored she is now pregnant. eww.  there are just some things that should not happen and that is one of them.  well anyway other than that i have been having a great time.  except for the bad week that i had in september.  it all started when my ex broke up with me on the wednesday, thursday was just a rubish day cause all of guys in my class were just talking bout their gf's and i was just like humph. i couldnt exactly tell them to shut up cause it was like 17 against 1 at the time cause one guy left midway.  lol.  then on the friday my grandmother died and then found out that the guy who broke up with me still liked me and also another one of my ex's. 

some how i have managed to keep my head up even with all this and so much more going on but i dont really remember much else but hey. what i dont understand is how bad things like this all tends to go off at like one time.  i still dont have any idea what im going to be doing for my 18th birthday though.  im thinking about having a party but i dont know where i should have it or maybe we should all just go out somewhere like clubbing in portsmouth or something i dunno.  i never have been good at thinking of these sort of things.  lol. well i have now up dated this so i think i shall go now.

bye :D

thursday till the 12th is spent being tormented by sisters and parents and friends who seem to be superglued together at the mouth and are inseperable like totally big time who say that i only moan not giving statements to the police and arguing with parents and siblings whilst thinking ill of one person whom shall remain unnamed although i still like him i think as more than a friend whilst helping others who have just broken up with their boyfriends or girlfriends and then giving advice to other people who have no sense of hygiene and then trying not to get into punch ups with next door neighbours whose heads are so far up their asses its any wonder that they know what the sun looks like. well moaning streak over i shall go now and do some tidying up cause their doesnt seem to be anything else to do as it is too late to bake another cake although i think that i have baked enough cakes. 12 over the past 2 days. bubi
